Request Description:
I request the following records maintained by the Office of Federal Student Aid that relate to the oversight of federal student loan servicers:

(1)	All final reports that describe the findings of secret shopper calls to federal student loan servicers;
(2)	All final reports that describe findings of monitoring reviews of service level agreements;
(3)	All final reports that describe the findings of quality assurance reviews; and
(4)	All final reports that describe the findings of any other type of review or examination by FSA of any federal student loan servicer.

Please limit your search to records produced after June 1, 2023.

